âœ… Features to Clone

Page/Feature	Description

Home Page	Banner, navigation bar, category links
Product Listing Page	Filterable and searchable list of items
Product Detail Page	Images, sizes, price, description
Cart Page	Add to cart, remove items, total cost
Login/Register Page	Simple authentication (optional)



